casebody.data:
Martin H. Burden, an Infant, by William J. Burden, His Guardian ad Litem, et al., Respondents-Appellants, v. Cadillac Developers Massapequa Corp., et al., Appellants, Schildenecht Lumber Co., Inc., Respondent, et al., Defendant. Argued January 9, 1964; decided February 20, 1964. *525William F. McNulty and Patrick F. Adams for appellants. Theodore D. Rothenberg, William A. Speckels and Leland Stuart Beck for respondents-appellants.

No appearance for respondent.

Judgment affirmed, without costs; no opinion.

Concur: Chief Judge Desmond and Judges Dye, Fuld, Van Voorhis, Burke, Scileppi and Bergan.
